All Implemented Interfaces:
AllInsideButtons, java.rmi.Remote, java.io.Serializable
public class AllInsideButtonsImpl
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements AllInsideButtons

The class >AllInsideButtonsImpl implements the elevator.rmi.InsideButtons interface used for adding remote action listeners interested in receiving events from the inside-buttons of all elevators or a group of elevators or one elevator. For example: 

 import java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject;
 import java.awt.event.*
 import elevator.rmi.*;
 ...
 public class MyListener extends UnicastRemoteObject
  implements RemoteActionListener {
     ...
     InsideButtons buttons = MakeAll.getAllInsideButtons();
     ...
     buttons.addActionListener((RemoteActionListener)this);
     ...
     public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent event) {
      System.out.println(event.getActionCommand());
     }
     ...
 }

1.0
